from sea to shining sea... ♪

42:31.635 --> 42:33.302
Commissioner.

42:33.304 --> 42:37.122
♪ Where's the promise
from sea to shining sea... ♪

42:37.124 --> 42:38.623
Irish, neat, water back.

42:38.625 --> 42:41.844
