42:44.431 --> 42:46.598
Buy you a drink?

42:46.600 --> 42:49.118
♪ Wherever this flag
is flown... ♪

42:49.120 --> 42:51.570
Irish, neat, water back.

42:51.572 --> 42:56.358
♪ We take care of our own

42:56.360 --> 43:00.329
♪ Wherever this flag's flown

43:00.331 --> 43:05.317
♪ We take care of our own...

43:05.319 --> 43:08.187
Officer Lee.

43:08.189 --> 43:11.039
Sir.

43:11.041 --> 43:15.711
♪ Wherever this flag's flown

43:15.713 --> 43:17.963
